## 🔄 Common Operations

### Restart the Application

```bash
# Development
{{#eq packageManager "npm"}}npm run dev{{else}}{{packageManager}} run dev{{/eq}}

# Production
{{#eq packageManager "npm"}}npm run build && npm start{{else}}{{packageManager}} run build && {{packageManager}} start{{/eq}}
```

### Clear Cache

```bash
{{#eq packageManager "npm"}}npm{{else}}{{packageManager}}{{/eq}} cache clean --force
rm -rf node_modules
{{packageManager}} install
```

