## 🐛 Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely Cause | Resolution |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Build fails | Outdated dependencies | Run `{{packageManager}} update` |
| Tests hang | Async timeout | Check for unhandled promises |
| Port in use | Another process bound to port | Kill process or change PORT env |

